An android application for viewing the status of the stations in the Oslo bysykkel system.

Uses gradle.properties for signing of apk.

To use gradle you need to create a the gradle properties with the following content

KEYSTORE_PATH=<Path to the keystore, relative to the root of the project>
KEYSTORE_PASSWORD=<Password of the keystore>
KEY_ALIAS=<The name of the key to use>
KEY_PASSWORD=<password for the key>


To build the apk
./gradlew build

To deploy to device
./gradlew installDebug
